ADDITIONAL CONDITIONS SPECIFIC TO THIS DATASET

1. ANONYMIZATION INTEGRITY. You agree not to attempt to re-identify the source
   institutions referenced by the regional cluster codes (e.g., MM-PSEC-1,
   PROV-PUB-1) from the released artifacts, nor to combine the released
   artifacts with external sources for that purpose. The school_alias field
   has been deliberately stripped from the public release; do not infer or
   reconstruct it.

2. NO INDIVIDUAL-LEVEL INFERENCE. The corpus is a collection of anonymous
   public posts. Per-post records reflect what was publicly written on the
   relevant Freedom Wall pages, not the verified beliefs, behaviors, or
   identities of any individual author. You agree not to use the data to
   profile, identify, or surveil individual posters.

3. ETHICAL USE. Use of the data is restricted to academic research, education,
   and non-commercial scholarly inquiry consistent with the data-minimization
   commitment articulated in the Method section of the accompanying manuscript
   (see Ethical considerations). The raw scraped corpus before anonymization
   is not released under any terms.

4. CITATION. If you use this data in published work, please cite the
   accompanying manuscript (see README.md for the citation block).
